description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 15, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 30, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Box for East, Stringalong for South, and Box for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40152-64742-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [30 Votes, Common]
